    <string name="help_2_q">How do I record habit data?</string>
    <string name="help_2_a">   Choose a habit from the list on the habits page, then scroll down to the "Data by Date" section.  Choose the date you want to enter data for, and tap the "Set Value" button.  Enter the data and click "Save."</string>
    <string name="help_3_q">How do I stop tracking a habit?</string>
